Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu/gfx10,11: use memcpy_to/fromio for MQDs
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: b3c942bb6c32a8ddc1d52ee6bc24b8cf732dddf4
